{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshnotificationui"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshnotificationui"]}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Stories UI","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController"]},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/StoryPage"],"title":"Payload model"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesDelegate"],"title":"Analytics"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesMediaPrefetcher"],"title":"Media pre-cache"}],"metadata":{"externalID":"PushwooshNotificationUI","symbolKind":"module","title":"PushwooshNotificationUI","role":"collection","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshNotificationUI"}],"roleHeading":"Framework"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A ready-made full-screen “stories” UI for an expanded push notification."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"PushwooshNotificationUI provides "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" — a drop-in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"UNNotificationContentExtension","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" view controller that renders an Instagram-style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"stories experience: full-bleed images, top progress bars, auto-advance, tap-zone","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"navigation, per-frame title\/subtitle, and an optional deep-link button.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The module links only UIKit, UserNotifications, and UserNotificationsUI (plus"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"CryptoKit for a stable cache key), so it adds no Pushwoosh Core\/Framework weight"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to your memory-constrained extension process.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Usage","text":"Usage","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In your Notification Content Extension:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import PushwooshNotificationUI","","class NotificationViewController: PushwooshStoriesViewController {}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then set these keys in the extension’s Info.plist:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNNotificationExtensionCategory"},{"type":"text","text":" = "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PW_STORIES"},{"type":"text","text":" (must match "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"aps.category"},{"text":")","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"UNNotificationExtensionUserInteractionEnabled","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" = ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"UNNotificationExtensionDefaultContentHidden","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" = "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNNotificationExtensionInitialContentSizeRatio"},{"text":" = e.g. ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1.5"},{"type":"text","text":" (keep in sync with "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController\/storyAspectRatio"},{"text":")","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSExtensionPrincipalClass"},{"text":" = ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"$(PRODUCT_MODULE_NAME).NotificationViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" (code-only, no storyboard)"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Payload","level":2,"anchor":"Payload","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The stories are described by a "},{"code":"pw_stories","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" block, alongside an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"aps.category"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"matching "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNNotificationExtensionCategory"},{"text":". The parser accepts the block either at","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"payload root"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g. via the Pushwoosh API "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ios_root_params"},{"text":") or inside the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"custom-data container "},{"code":"u","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" \/ ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userdata"},{"type":"text","text":" (the Pushwoosh API "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"data"},{"text":" field — delivered as","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a dictionary or a JSON-encoded string). The root form on the device looks like this:"}]},{"syntax":"json","code":["{","  \"aps\": { \"category\": \"PW_STORIES\" },","  \"pw_stories\": { \"pages\": [","    { \"image\": \"https:\/\/...\/1.jpg\", \"duration\": 5.0,","      \"link\": \"myapp:\/\/sale\", \"button_title\": \"Buy\",","      \"title\": \"Summer Sale\", \"subtitle\": \"Up to 70% off\" },","    { \"image\": \"https:\/\/...\/2.jpg\" }","  ]}","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sent through the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"data"},{"text":" API field instead (recommended, since it does not depend on","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ios_root_params"},{"type":"text","text":"), the same block arrives nested under "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"u"},{"text":" — while ","type":"text"},{"code":"aps.category","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"mutable-content"},{"type":"text","text":" for the pre-cache path) still go through "},{"code":"ios_root_params.aps","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as there is no dedicated request field for them. The relevant createMessage fields:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"json","code":["{","  \"ios_root_params\": { \"aps\": { \"category\": \"PW_STORIES\", \"mutable-content\": 1 } },","  \"data\": { \"pw_stories\": { \"pages\": [ { \"image\": \"https:\/\/...\/1.jpg\" } ] } }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The parser tries the root first, then ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"u"},{"type":"text","text":" \/ "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userdata"},{"type":"text","text":", so both delivery styles work"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and old pushes keep rendering."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Every field except ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"image"},{"type":"text","text":" is optional. "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"link"},{"text":" (like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"image"},{"type":"text","text":") must include a URL"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"scheme. A missing, empty, or malformed payload falls back to the default content","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(the alert body) without crashing — override "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController\/showDefaultContent(for:)","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"text":"Analytics","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Analytics"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Set ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController\/storiesDelegate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" to observe lifecycle and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"engagement and forward it to your analytics (the module itself sends nothing):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class NotificationViewController: PushwooshStoriesViewController, PushwooshStoriesDelegate {","    override func viewDidLoad() {","        super.viewDidLoad()","        storiesDelegate = self","    }","    func storiesViewController(_ c: PushwooshStoriesViewController, didTapActionFor page: StoryPage, at index: Int) {","        \/\/ forward the per-page click to your backend","    }","}"]},{"level":2,"text":"Instant \/ offline first frame (App Group pre-cache)","anchor":"Instant--offline-first-frame-App-Group-pre-cache","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To make the first frame appear instantly (and offline), pre-download the media in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a Notification "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Service","type":"text"}]},{"text":" Extension into a shared App Group container that the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Content Extension reads from:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enable the "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"App Groups"}]},{"type":"text","text":" capability (same id) on both the Service and Content"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"extensions, and override ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesViewController\/appGroupIdentifier"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"From the Service Extension’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"didReceive(_:withContentHandler:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", call"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI\/documentation\/PushwooshNotificationUI\/PushwooshStoriesMediaPrefetcher\/prefetch(userInfo:appGroupIdentifier:completion:)"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Send the push with "},{"code":"mutable-content: 1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so the Service Extension runs."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Without this, the module still works — images download on display instead.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshNotificationUI/documentation/PushwooshNotificationUI/PushwooshStoriesMediaPrefetcher":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Entry point for a Notification "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Service"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" Extension: pre-downloads the story media referenced","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"by a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pw_stories"},{"type":"text","text":" payload into the shared App Group container, so the Content Extension can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"render the first frame instantly and offline. Call from ","type":"text"},{"code":"didReceive(_:withContentHandler:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":